{"tid":1354552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本上大家呢幾日唔好上連登就唔會俾人帶到風","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T07:20:06.000Z","uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44cfca2aac5257fae7613716e310c85bd6affce4","tid":1354552,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"淨係記得27號要出元朗full gear 就得了，唔駛再上連登看什麼分析被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n從依家到27號我唔再上來or看呢到既post<br />\n<br />\n27見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8e48d9a09a297dd5951f54651ea9d4d609174a","tid":1354552,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44cfca2aac5257fae7613716e310c85bd6affce4","tid":1354552,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"淨係記得27號要出元朗full gear 就得了，唔駛再上連登看什麼分析被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n從依家到27號我唔再上來or看呢到既post<br />\n<br />\n27見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"[727光復元朗]  727元朗反黑反恐行動部署提議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354479</a><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下我嘅提議～<br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗 (副題：元朗反黑反恐行動) <br />\n口號：肅清鄉黑，除暴安良 <br />\n目的：以武力震懾元朗鄉黑勢力，保障元朗社區安全。 <br />\n<br />\n727香港人嘅主要目標有 <br />\n1. 針對鄉黑黃賭毒勢力經濟進行破壞 (首要目標：黃色經濟) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得除咗元朗有黑社會之外。 <br />\n元朗區同屯門公園一樣，有色情流鶯問題。 <br />\n掃鄉黑圍村個時，幫埋元朗區搞掂埋黃色問題。 <br />\n<br />\n建議： <br />\n進行141洗樓行動，對流鶯進行驅趕。 <br />\n為咗cut班鄉黑嘅收入 <br />\n<br />\n一樓一地址141個網有架啦。我睇下post唔post出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都可以係一樓一門口貼下紙仔 <br />\n個人推介可以貼五十路林鄭av封面圖同鄭若驊大波圖係一樓一舊樓門口。 <br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以注意睇下啲粉紅光管，啲門口cam可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n同埋call埋入境處舉報有人違反逗留條件，入境處都有執法嘅權力。 <br />\n<br />\n舉報違反入境條例罪行 <a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=32d7b0b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線： (852) 2824 1551 (舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號) <br />\n<br />\n人地已經ready <br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻雀館大家睇下可以點搞，我唔熟"},{"pid":"a65bc81f34169792943f3c698a8d700fd2036f1e","tid":1354552,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b663d30ee179370ecfa96ca2fab82800cc78541f","tid":1354552,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"地形分析：<br />\n【光復元朗】作為一個元朗居民我有啲野想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351965</a><br />\n我係一個由細到大都係圍村長大嘅港女，我有講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354569/page/1</a>"}]}